arena-video/

# Accidental duplicates from macOS "Save As" and Windows "Save a Copy":
# catches the "<name> 2.<ext>" / "<name> - Copy.<ext>" / "<name> (1).<ext>"
# pattern that produced four orphan files (memory 2.py, DebateMode 2.tsx,
# package-lock 2.json, memory_v2.py) in the chore cleanup. Patterns here
# target filenames only — directories like "release 2026" or files like
# "release-v2.md" (no space before 2) still commit normally.
* [0-9].*
* - Copy.*
* - Copy (*.*
* (*).*


